Arduino Developing Base Project

I've started this project in order to be able to easily start develop and deploy arduino application.
It exports a base Makefile and ANT tasks.

USEFUL LINKS

http://arduino.cc/
http://www.nongnu.org/avr-libc/user-manual/index.html


DEPENDENCIES
Arduino sdk contains all you need: avr and avrdude (for both linux and windows)
           
HOW TO USE    
see the wiki for details.





